[
  {
    "id": "dlg_001",
    "speaker": "char_zhang_chao_tang",
    "speaker_name": "张朝唐",
    "listener": "char_zhang_kang",
    "text": "浡泥国⋯⋯其国之民崇佛像，好斋沐。凡见唐人至其国，甚有爱敬。有醉者，则扶归家寝宿，以礼待之若故旧。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 13,
    "line_end": 13
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_002",
    "speaker": "char_zhang_kang",
    "speaker_name": "张康",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "喂，店家，店家！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 29,
    "line_end": 29
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_003",
    "speaker": "char_zhang_kang",
    "speaker_name": "张康",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "喂，店家，店家",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 29,
    "line_end": 29
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_004",
    "speaker": "char_zhang_chao_tang",
    "speaker_name": "张朝唐",
    "listener": "char_zhang_kang",
    "text": "到别处看看。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 33,
    "line_end": 33
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_005",
    "speaker": "char_zhang_kang",
    "speaker_name": "张康",
    "listener": "char_zhang_chao_tang",
    "text": "公子，你瞧！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 35,
    "line_end": 35
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_006",
    "speaker": "char_zhang_chao_tang",
    "speaker_name": "张朝唐",
    "listener": "char_zhang_kang",
    "text": "咱们借宿去。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 35,
    "line_end": 35
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_007",
    "speaker": "char_zhang_chao_tang",
    "speaker_name": "张朝唐",
    "listener": "char_zhang_kang",
    "text": "倘若那是贼窟，岂不是自投死路？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 37,
    "line_end": 37
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_008",
    "speaker": "char_zhang_kang",
    "speaker_name": "张康",
    "listener": "char_zhang_chao_tang",
    "text": "那么别去吧。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 37,
    "line_end": 37
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_009",
    "speaker": "char_zhang_chao_tang",
    "speaker_name": "张朝唐",
    "listener": "char_zhang_kang",
    "text": "先悄悄过去瞧一瞧。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 37,
    "line_end": 37
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_010",
    "speaker": "char_zhang_chao_tang",
    "speaker_name": "张朝唐",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我们是过路客人，想在府上借宿一晚。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 39,
    "line_end": 39
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_152",
    "speaker": "char_cui_qiu_shan",
    "speaker_name": "崔秋山",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你们是曹太监的手下，到这里来干什么？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 2,
    "line_start": 3,
    "line_end": 3
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_153",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_cui_qiu_shan",
    "text": "你是说我吗？开什么玩笑？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 2,
    "line_start": 7,
    "line_end": 7
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_154",
    "speaker": "char_cui_qiu_shan",
    "speaker_name": "崔秋山",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "哼，开玩笑！你们两个鬼鬼祟祟在客店里商量，要混进山宗来，又说已禀告了曹太监，要派兵来一网打尽，这些话都给我听见啦！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 2,
    "line_start": 7,
    "line_end": 7
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_155",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_tian_jian_xiu",
    "text": "王自用想收并山宗的朋友，成为第三十七营，居心险恶，那一个不知道了？你想来造谣生事，挑拨离间，那可不成。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 2,
    "line_start": 9,
    "line_end": 9
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_156",
    "speaker": "char_tian_jian_xiu",
    "speaker_name": "田见秀",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "阁下是谁？是山宗的朋友么？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 2,
    "line_start": 11,
    "line_end": 11
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_157",
    "speaker": "char_sun_zhong_shou",
    "speaker_name": "孙仲寿",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "朋友是袁督师旧部么？我怎地没见过？你是那一位总兵手下？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 2,
    "line_start": 13,
    "line_end": 13
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_158",
    "speaker": "char_cui_qiu_shan",
    "speaker_name": "崔秋山",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你是不是太监，大家瞧瞧！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 2,
    "line_start": 23,
    "line_end": 23
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_159",
    "speaker": "char_sun_zhong_shou",
    "speaker_name": "孙仲寿",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "曹太监派你们来干什么？还有多少同党？怎么混进来的？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 2,
    "line_start": 25,
    "line_end": 25
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_160",
    "speaker": "char_sun_zhong_shou",
    "speaker_name": "孙仲寿",
    "listener": "char_tian_jian_xiu",
    "text": "若不是三位发现奸贼，我们大祸临头还不知道。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 2,
    "line_start": 27,
    "line_end": 27
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_161",
    "speaker": "char_tian_jian_xiu",
    "speaker_name": "田见秀",
    "listener": "char_sun_zhong_shou",
    "text": "那也是碰巧。我们在道上遇见这两个家伙，见他们神色古怪，身手又甚灵便，晚上便到客店去查探，侥幸查明了他们的底细。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 2,
    "line_start": 27,
    "line_end": 27
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_294",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": "char_an_da_niang",
    "text": "崔叔叔呢？他好么？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_295",
    "speaker": "char_an_da_niang",
    "speaker_name": "安大娘",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "崔叔叔没事，你放心。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 7,
    "line_end": 7
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_296",
    "speaker": "char_an_da_niang",
    "speaker_name": "安大娘",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "承志，我一见你就很喜欢，就当你是我的亲儿子一般。今日你不顾性命的相救小慧，我更加永远忘不了你。今晚我要到一个很远的地方去。你跟着哑伯伯去。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 9,
    "line_end": 9
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_297",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": "char_an_da_niang",
    "text": "安婶婶，我要跟你一起去。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 9,
    "line_end": 9
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_298",
    "speaker": "char_an_da_niang",
    "speaker_name": "安大娘",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "我也舍不得你啊。我要哑伯伯带你到一个人那里。他曾教过你崔叔叔武功。你崔叔叔只跟他学了两个月武艺，就这般了得。这位老前辈的武功天下无双，我要你去跟他学。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 9,
    "line_end": 9
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_299",
    "speaker": "char_an_da_niang",
    "speaker_name": "安大娘",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "这位老前辈脾气很古怪，你不听话，他固然不喜欢，太听话了，他又嫌你太蠢，没自己主意，只好碰你的缘法吧。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 13,
    "line_end": 13
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_300",
    "speaker": "char_an_da_niang",
    "speaker_name": "安大娘",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "等你武功学好，成为大孩子时，别忘记安婶婶和小慧妹子！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 13,
    "line_end": 13
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_301",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": "char_an_da_niang",
    "text": "我永远不会忘记。要是那位老前辈肯收我，安婶婶你有空时，就带小慧妹妹来瞧瞧我。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 15,
    "line_end": 15
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_302",
    "speaker": "char_an_da_niang",
    "speaker_name": "安大娘",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "好的，我会时时记着你。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 15,
    "line_end": 15
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_303",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "师父，你老人家可来啦！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 31,
    "line_end": 31
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_471",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": "char_mu_sang_dao_ren",
    "text": "到底秘笈中写着什么？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 3,
    "line_end": 3
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_472",
    "speaker": "char_mu_sang_dao_ren",
    "speaker_name": "木桑道人",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "何必生这么大的气，破了阵法也就是了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 13,
    "line_end": 13
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_473",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": "char_mu_sang_dao_ren",
    "text": "师父常教我说，自己武功既强，便须时时存着‘手下容情，留有余地’的念头。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 13,
    "line_end": 13
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_474",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "金蛇郎君并未留言赠我此剑，我见此宝剑，便欲据为己有，未免贪心，还是让它在此伴着旧主吧。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 27,
    "line_end": 27
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_475",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "重宝秘术，付与有缘，入我门来，遇祸莫怨",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 29,
    "line_end": 29
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_476",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "人间假意多而真情罕见，种种试探，欲明对方真意所在，而真意殊不易知，此所以惆怅长夜而柔肠百转欲断也。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 37,
    "line_end": 37
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_477",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "别道人家有无真情，即令自己，此招终归何处，自家总亦不知。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 37,
    "line_end": 37
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_478",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "师父常告诫，修习武功，须防走火入魔，一旦入魔，精神纷乱，不易收拾。金蛇郎君想到这里，已近乎走火入魔，我可不能跟着学了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 37,
    "line_end": 37
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_479",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我混元功早已练成，为了这部金蛇秘笈，却在山上多耽了两个月功夫。师父曾说金蛇郎君为人怪僻，他的书观之无益。一招招式连自己也不知击向何处，心意不定，那算是什么武功招数？这招‘意假情真’，也委实巧妙之至。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 39,
    "line_end": 39
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_480",
    "speaker": "char_mu_sang_dao_ren",
    "speaker_name": "木桑道人",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "眼不见为净，我一把火将它烧了便是。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 41,
    "line_end": 41
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_643",
    "speaker": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "speaker_name": "夏青青",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "月白风清，这么好的夜晚。袁兄雅人，不怕辜负了大好时光吗？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 3,
    "line_end": 3
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_644",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "text": "好，我穿衣就来。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_645",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "text": "真是神仙般的好地方。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 11,
    "line_end": 11
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_646",
    "speaker": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "speaker_name": "夏青青",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "这些花是我亲手种的，除了妈妈和小菊之外，谁也不许来。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 11,
    "line_end": 11
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_647",
    "speaker": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "speaker_name": "夏青青",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "这里不能吃荤。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 13,
    "line_end": 13
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_648",
    "speaker": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "speaker_name": "夏青青",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "我吹首曲子给你听。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 15,
    "line_end": 15
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_649",
    "speaker": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "speaker_name": "夏青青",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "你爱什么曲子？我吹给你听。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 17,
    "line_end": 17
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_650",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "text": "我什么曲子都不知。你懂得真多，怎地这等聪明？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 17,
    "line_end": 17
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_651",
    "speaker": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "speaker_name": "夏青青",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "你觉得好听么？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 19,
    "line_end": 19
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_652",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "text": "世界上竟有这般好听的箫声，以前我做梦也没想到过。这曲子叫什么名字？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 19,
    "line_end": 19
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_899",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "那是二十年前的事了，那时我二十六岁。爹爹叫我到扬州去给六叔做帮手。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 3,
    "line_end": 3
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_900",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "原来静岩温氏五祖本有六兄弟。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 3,
    "line_end": 3
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_901",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "我到了扬州，没遇上六叔。一天晚上出去做案子，不小心失了手。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 3,
    "line_end": 3
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_902",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "不知是做什么案子？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 3,
    "line_end": 3
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_903",
    "speaker": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "speaker_name": "夏青青",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我还道你是不怕死的。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 9,
    "line_end": 9
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_904",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "我便向他行礼道谢。那人骄傲得很，也不还礼，说道：‘我姓夏，你是棋仙派姓温的了？’我点头说是，这时见他腰间挂着那柄削断我铐镣的兵刃，弯弯曲曲的似乎是柄剑，只是剑头分叉，模样很古怪。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 13,
    "line_end": 13
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_905",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "那便是那柄金蛇剑了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 15,
    "line_end": 15
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_906",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "这位金蛇郎君大有豪气。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 21,
    "line_end": 21
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_907",
    "speaker": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "speaker_name": "夏青青",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "这人真是英雄豪杰。好威风，好气概！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 21,
    "line_end": 21
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_908",
    "speaker": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "speaker_name": "夏青青",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "的确不坏，杀了个大闺女，带来一口大箱子。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 25,
    "line_end": 25
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_1048",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "刚才那位老爷子说过，只要动了三根金条，全部黄金奉还，兄弟在这里谢过。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_1049",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "都捡起来吧。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_1050",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "怎么？你也要见过输赢是不是？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 7,
    "line_end": 7
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_1051",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "希敏，退下！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 9,
    "line_end": 9
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_1052",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "恭喜发财！掌柜的宝号是什么字号？大老板一向做什么生意？想必是生意兴隆通四海， 财源茂盛达三江。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 9,
    "line_end": 9
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_1053",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "谁跟你开玩笑？在下姓荣名彩，忝任游龙帮帮主。还没请教阁下的万儿。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 9,
    "line_end": 9
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_1054",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "贱姓黄，便是‘黄金万两’之黄，彩头甚好。草字单名一个真字，取其真不二价、货真价实的意思。一两银子的东西，小号决不敢要一两另一文，那真是老幼咸宜，童叟无欺。大老板有什么生意，请你帮趁帮趁。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 9,
    "line_end": 9
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_1055",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "啊哟，咱们做生意的，金子可不能不要。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 11,
    "line_end": 11
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_1056",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "要拿金子，可没那么容易。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 13,
    "line_end": 13
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_1057",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "黄师伯留神。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 19,
    "line_end": 19
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_1226",
    "speaker": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "speaker_name": "夏青青",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "干么不追上去再挥手？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 8,
    "line_start": 3,
    "line_end": 3
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_1227",
    "speaker": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "speaker_name": "夏青青",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "这般恋恋不舍，又怎不跟她一起去？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 8,
    "line_start": 3,
    "line_end": 3
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_1228",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "text": "我小时候遇到危难，承她妈妈相救，我们从小就在一块儿玩的。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 8,
    "line_start": 3,
    "line_end": 3
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_1229",
    "speaker": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "speaker_name": "夏青青",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "那就叫做青梅竹马了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 8,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_1230",
    "speaker": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "speaker_name": "夏青青",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "你要破五行阵，干么不用旁的兵刃，定要用她头上的玉簪？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 8,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_1231",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "text": "我使一根一碰就碎的玉簪，好教你五位爷爷心无所忌，便出手进攻，招式中就露出破绽。他们倘若只守不攻，此阵难破。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 8,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_1232",
    "speaker": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "speaker_name": "夏青青",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "难道我就没簪子吗？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 8,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_1233",
    "speaker": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "speaker_name": "夏青青",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "你跟她这么有说有笑的，见了我就闷闷不乐。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 8,
    "line_start": 7,
    "line_end": 7
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_1234",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "text": "我几时闷闷不乐了？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 8,
    "line_start": 7,
    "line_end": 7
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_1235",
    "speaker": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "speaker_name": "夏青青",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "人家的妈妈好，在你小时候救你疼你，我可是个没妈妈的人。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 8,
    "line_start": 7,
    "line_end": 7
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_1548",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "金蛇郎君不能来了，由他公子和兄弟前来，给各位做个和事老。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 9,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_1549",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "爹，就是他！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 9,
    "line_start": 9,
    "line_end": 9
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_1550",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "你叫什么名字？谁叫你到这里来多事？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 9,
    "line_start": 11,
    "line_end": 11
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_1551",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我虽然年纪小过你，可比你长着一辈，待会说出来，瞧你还敢不敢无礼？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 9,
    "line_start": 13,
    "line_end": 13
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_1552",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "在下姓袁。承金蛇郎君夏大侠之命来见焦帮主。今日得有机缘拜见各位前辈英雄，甚是荣幸。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 9,
    "line_start": 13,
    "line_end": 13
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_1553",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "什么金蛇铁蛇，快给我下去，别在这里碍手碍脚。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 9,
    "line_start": 17,
    "line_end": 17
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_1554",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "等一下， 且听他胡说些什么。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 9,
    "line_start": 23,
    "line_end": 23
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_1555",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "这位爷台将两封信扯得粉碎，不知是什么用意？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 9,
    "line_start": 25,
    "line_end": 25
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_1556",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "这是捏造的假信，这姓焦的妄想藉此骗人，不扯碎了留着干么？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 9,
    "line_start": 29,
    "line_end": 29
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_1557",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我们来时，金蛇大侠曾提到书信内容。这两封信虽已粉碎，这位大师与这位爷台是看过的。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 9,
    "line_start": 29,
    "line_end": 29
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_1905",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_mu_sang_dao_ren",
    "text": "贪睡猫，到这时候才起身，道长可等得急坏了，快下棋，快下棋。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 10,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_1906",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_mu_sang_dao_ren",
    "text": "道长给你什么好处？你这般出力帮他找对手。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 10,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_1907",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "道长教了我一套功夫。这功夫啊，可真妙啦。别人向你拳打脚踢，你却只管跟他捉迷藏，东一溜，西一晃，他再也别想打到你。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 10,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_1908",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_mu_sang_dao_ren",
    "text": "下棋倒也可以，可是你得把这套功夫转教给我。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 10,
    "line_start": 7,
    "line_end": 7
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_1909",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "好哇，这叫见者有份，你跟我讲起黑道上的规矩来啦。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 10,
    "line_start": 7,
    "line_end": 7
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_1910",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_mu_sang_dao_ren",
    "text": "你小朋友叫你呢，快去吧！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 10,
    "line_start": 9,
    "line_end": 9
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_1911",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "快来，我把道长教的功夫跟你说。他教的时候我压根儿就不懂。他说：‘你硬记着，将来慢慢儿就懂了。’我怕再过一阵就全给忘了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 10,
    "line_start": 11,
    "line_end": 11
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_1912",
    "speaker": "char_mu_sang_dao_ren",
    "speaker_name": "木桑道人",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "你大师哥为人滑稽，不免有点浮躁。二师哥却木讷深沉，用功尤为扎实。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 10,
    "line_start": 15,
    "line_end": 15
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_1913",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "text": "他们是我师哥师嫂，今晚我只挨打不还手，你瞧着定要生气，岂不要坏我事？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 10,
    "line_start": 23,
    "line_end": 23
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_1914",
    "speaker": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "speaker_name": "夏青青",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "你让他们三招也就是了，干么老不还手？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 10,
    "line_start": 23,
    "line_end": 23
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_2211",
    "speaker": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "speaker_name": "夏青青",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "他们伤了这许多人，只在铁箱外面摸得几下，你说是赚了还是蚀了，得请你大师哥用铁算盘来算一下了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 3,
    "line_end": 3
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_2212",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "要拉拢山东、河北这两批英豪，这次看来是不成的了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 3,
    "line_end": 3
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_2213",
    "speaker": "char_hong_sheng_hai",
    "speaker_name": "洪胜海",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "赶路的老百姓。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_2214",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_hong_sheng_hai",
    "text": "干么这里有血迹，有兵器？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_2215",
    "speaker": "char_hong_sheng_hai",
    "speaker_name": "洪胜海",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "正有强人拦路打劫，幸得官兵到来，吓退了强人。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_2216",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_hong_sheng_hai",
    "text": "那些是什么东西？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 7,
    "line_end": 7
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_2217",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_hong_sheng_hai",
    "text": "打开来瞧瞧。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 7,
    "line_end": 7
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_2218",
    "speaker": "char_hong_sheng_hai",
    "speaker_name": "洪胜海",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "是些随身衣物，没什么特别物事。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 7,
    "line_end": 7
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_2219",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_hong_sheng_hai",
    "text": "我说打开，就打开，啰唆什么？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 7,
    "line_end": 7
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_2220",
    "speaker": "char_hong_sheng_hai",
    "speaker_name": "洪胜海",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "又没带违禁犯法的东西，瞧什么？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 7,
    "line_end": 7
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_2383",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "帮主，再过四天，就是孟伯飞孟老爷子的六十大寿，你不去了吧？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 12,
    "line_start": 9,
    "line_end": 9
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_2384",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "我要随盟主上京，祝寿是不能去了。我是礼到人不到，已备了一份礼，叫人送去保定府。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 12,
    "line_start": 9,
    "line_end": 9
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_2385",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "兄弟的礼也早已送去。孟老爷子知道我们不到，必是身有要事，决不能见怪。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 12,
    "line_start": 9,
    "line_end": 9
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_2386",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "这盖孟尝在北五省大大有名，既是他寿辰在即，何不乘机结交一番？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 12,
    "line_start": 9,
    "line_end": 9
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_2387",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "孟老爷子兄弟是久仰了，原来日内就是他老人家六十大庆，兄弟想前去祝贺，各位以为怎样？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 12,
    "line_start": 9,
    "line_end": 9
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_2388",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "盟主给他这么大面子，孟老爷子一定乐极。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 12,
    "line_start": 9,
    "line_end": 9
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_2389",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "添酒添肉，快快！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 12,
    "line_start": 13,
    "line_end": 13
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_2390",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "大师父，你要喝酒，别人也要喝啊。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 12,
    "line_start": 15,
    "line_end": 15
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_2391",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我自叫店小二，干你屁事？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 12,
    "line_start": 15,
    "line_end": 15
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_2392",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "从来没见过这般凶狠的出家人。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 12,
    "line_start": 15,
    "line_end": 15
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_2658",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_he_hong_yao",
    "text": "我找得你好苦，舍得烧你吗？咱们来叙叙旧情吧！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 13,
    "line_start": 3,
    "line_end": 3
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_2659",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "好啊，谋杀亲夫！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 13,
    "line_start": 3,
    "line_end": 3
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_2660",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "听这姓安的口气，一时不致伤害于她，我且多探听一会，再出手相救。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 13,
    "line_start": 7,
    "line_end": 7
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_2661",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "胡老三，进去点火！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 13,
    "line_start": 9,
    "line_end": 9
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_2662",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_he_hong_yao",
    "text": "你说再也不要见我，这可不见了么？瞧瞧我，白头发多了几根吧？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 13,
    "line_start": 9,
    "line_end": 9
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_2663",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_he_hong_yao",
    "text": "好啊，十多年不见，脸蛋儿倒还雪白粉嫩的。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 13,
    "line_start": 13,
    "line_end": 13
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_2664",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_he_hong_yao",
    "text": "小慧呢？我这些年来天天想念她。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 13,
    "line_start": 15,
    "line_end": 15
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_2665",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_he_hong_yao",
    "text": "你我少年夫妻，大家火气大，一时反目，分别了这许多年，现今总该和好如初了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 13,
    "line_start": 15,
    "line_end": 15
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_2666",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_he_hong_yao",
    "text": "你瞧我十多年来，并没另娶，何曾有一时一刻忘记你？难道你连一点夫妻之情也没有么？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 13,
    "line_start": 15,
    "line_end": 15
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_2667",
    "speaker": "char_he_hong_yao",
    "speaker_name": "何红药",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我爹爹和哥哥是怎么死的，你忘记了吗？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 13,
    "line_start": 15,
    "line_end": 15
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_2876",
    "speaker": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "speaker_name": "夏青青",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "承志哥哥，鞑子皇帝刺得到果然好，刺不到也就罢了，你自己可千万要保重。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 14,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_2877",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "在我玉真子手下也想逃命么？痴心妄想！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 14,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_2878",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "你叫什么名字？是木桑道人的弟子吗？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 14,
    "line_start": 7,
    "line_end": 7
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_2879",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "你怎地会铁剑门的步法？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 14,
    "line_start": 7,
    "line_end": 7
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_2880",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你是汉人，怎地反帮鞑子？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 14,
    "line_start": 7,
    "line_end": 7
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_2881",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "倔强小子，死到临头，还在胡说。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 14,
    "line_start": 7,
    "line_end": 7
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_2882",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "啊，你是华山派穆老猴儿门下的小猴儿，是不是？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 14,
    "line_start": 9,
    "line_end": 9
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_2883",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "好剑法，小猴儿不坏！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 14,
    "line_start": 9,
    "line_end": 9
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_2884",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你这做汉奸的贼道！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 14,
    "line_start": 11,
    "line_end": 11
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_2885",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "老猴儿也不是我对手，你小猴儿更加不用想。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 14,
    "line_start": 11,
    "line_end": 11
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3051",
    "speaker": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "speaker_name": "夏青青",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "承志哥哥，多谢你今天全心全意的陪我。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 15,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3052",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "text": "青弟，多谢你今天全心全意的陪我。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 15,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3053",
    "speaker": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "speaker_name": "夏青青",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "我那一天都是全心全意的陪你，你就不是。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 15,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3054",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "text": "我怎么不是？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 15,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3055",
    "speaker": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "speaker_name": "夏青青",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "承志哥哥，我求你一件事，行不行？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 15,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3056",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "text": "不必问，你说了就行。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 15,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3057",
    "speaker": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "speaker_name": "夏青青",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "男子汉大丈夫，七省英豪的盟主，说过了的话可不许赖。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 15,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3058",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "text": "我就算不是七省盟主，对你说过了的也必不会赖。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 15,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3059",
    "speaker": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "speaker_name": "夏青青",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "承志哥哥，我求你别老是牵记着那个阿九。这些日子来，不论做什么事的时候，你总是在想念阿九。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 15,
    "line_start": 7,
    "line_end": 7
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3060",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "text": "天大冤枉！我几时想着她了？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 15,
    "line_start": 7,
    "line_end": 7
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3210",
    "speaker": "char_jiao_wan_er",
    "speaker_name": "焦宛儿",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "袁相公，可以动手了么？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 16,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3211",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": "char_jiao_wan_er",
    "text": "叫大伙守在外面，咱们几个人先去一探。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 16,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3212",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "姓闵的，出来瞧瞧，是谁来啦！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 16,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3213",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "点了火把进去！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 16,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3214",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "一命还一命，杀闵子华一人已经够了，不必让洞玄也陪在这里。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 16,
    "line_start": 15,
    "line_end": 15
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3215",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "我师兄弟不知何事得罪了阁下，如此苦苦相逼？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 16,
    "line_start": 21,
    "line_end": 21
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3216",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "仙都门下子字辈弟子洞玄收执",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 16,
    "line_start": 21,
    "line_end": 21
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3217",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "我学艺不精，不是你对手，死给你看便了。快把匕首还我！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 16,
    "line_start": 23,
    "line_end": 23
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3218",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "待得料理清楚，自然还你。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 16,
    "line_start": 23,
    "line_end": 23
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3219",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "你要杀就杀，不能如此欺人！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 16,
    "line_start": 23,
    "line_end": 23
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3449",
    "speaker": "char_hong_sheng_hai",
    "speaker_name": "洪胜海",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "这位是曹公公。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 17,
    "line_start": 7,
    "line_end": 7
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3450",
    "speaker": "char_cao_hua_chun",
    "speaker_name": "曹化淳",
    "listener": "char_hong_sheng_hai",
    "text": "别多礼啦，请坐，睿王爷安好？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 17,
    "line_start": 7,
    "line_end": 7
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3451",
    "speaker": "char_hong_sheng_hai",
    "speaker_name": "洪胜海",
    "listener": "char_cao_hua_chun",
    "text": "王爷福体安好。王爷命小人问公公好。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 17,
    "line_start": 7,
    "line_end": 7
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3452",
    "speaker": "char_cao_hua_chun",
    "speaker_name": "曹化淳",
    "listener": "char_hong_sheng_hai",
    "text": "我这几根老骨头，却也多承王爷惦记。洪老哥远道而来，不知王爷有什么嘱咐。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 17,
    "line_start": 7,
    "line_end": 7
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3453",
    "speaker": "char_hong_sheng_hai",
    "speaker_name": "洪胜海",
    "listener": "char_cao_hua_chun",
    "text": "王爷要请问公公，大事筹划得怎样了？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 17,
    "line_start": 7,
    "line_end": 7
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3454",
    "speaker": "char_cao_hua_chun",
    "speaker_name": "曹化淳",
    "listener": "char_hong_sheng_hai",
    "text": "我们皇上的性子，真是固执得要命。我进言了好几次，皇上总说借兵灭寇，后患太多，只求两国议和罢兵，等大明灭了流寇，重重酬谢睿王爷。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 17,
    "line_start": 9,
    "line_end": 9
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3455",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "皇帝不肯借兵，满洲人却心急要借，显是不怀好意了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 17,
    "line_start": 11,
    "line_end": 11
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3456",
    "speaker": "char_cao_hua_chun",
    "speaker_name": "曹化淳",
    "listener": "char_hong_sheng_hai",
    "text": "兄弟，你别急，一计不成，二计又生呀！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 17,
    "line_start": 13,
    "line_end": 13
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3457",
    "speaker": "char_hong_sheng_hai",
    "speaker_name": "洪胜海",
    "listener": "char_cao_hua_chun",
    "text": "是，是。曹公公足智多谋，我们王爷赞不绝口，常说有曹公公在宫中主持，何愁大事不成。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 17,
    "line_start": 13,
    "line_end": 13
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3458",
    "speaker": "char_hong_sheng_hai",
    "speaker_name": "洪胜海",
    "listener": "char_cao_hua_chun",
    "text": "王爷有几件薄礼，命小人带来，请公公笑纳。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 17,
    "line_start": 15,
    "line_end": 15
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3718",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_a_jiu",
    "text": "殿下，你没事么？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 18,
    "line_start": 3,
    "line_end": 3
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3719",
    "speaker": "char_a_jiu",
    "speaker_name": "阿九",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我睡啦，有什么事？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 18,
    "line_start": 3,
    "line_end": 3
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3720",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_a_jiu",
    "text": "有人见到刺客偷进了咱们寝宫。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 18,
    "line_start": 3,
    "line_end": 3
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3721",
    "speaker": "char_a_jiu",
    "speaker_name": "阿九",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "胡说八道，什么刺客？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 18,
    "line_start": 3,
    "line_end": 3
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3722",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_a_jiu",
    "text": "殿下，让奴婢们进来瞧瞧吧！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 18,
    "line_start": 3,
    "line_end": 3
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3723",
    "speaker": "char_a_jiu",
    "speaker_name": "阿九",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "若有刺客，我还能这么安安稳稳的么？快走，别在这里胡闹！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 18,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3724",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我要闯出，有谁能挡？但这一来可污了公主的名声，万万使不得。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 18,
    "line_start": 7,
    "line_end": 7
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3725",
    "speaker": "char_a_jiu",
    "speaker_name": "阿九",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "不怕，在这里待一会儿好啦。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 18,
    "line_start": 9,
    "line_end": 9
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3726",
    "speaker": "char_cao_hua_chun",
    "speaker_name": "曹化淳",
    "listener": "char_a_jiu",
    "text": "奴婢是曹化淳。皇上听说有刺客进宫，很不放心，命奴婢来向殿下问安。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 18,
    "line_start": 11,
    "line_end": 11
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3727",
    "speaker": "char_a_jiu",
    "speaker_name": "阿九",
    "listener": "char_cao_hua_chun",
    "text": "不敢劳动曹公公。你请回吧，我这里没事。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 18,
    "line_start": 11,
    "line_end": 11
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3918",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "师父，她醒了一会，老是问你，这时又睡着了。她正在梦里跟你相会呢！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 19,
    "line_start": 3,
    "line_end": 3
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3919",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "相公，沙寨主拿住了太监王相尧，已率人打开了宣武门！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 19,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3920",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "义军进城了么？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 19,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3921",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "刘宗敏将军已带队进来了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 19,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3922",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "好极了，咱们快去迎接。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 19,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3923",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "金蛇王攻破正阳门，横天王带队进城。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 19,
    "line_start": 9,
    "line_end": 9
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3924",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "齐化门开了，左金王的兵进来了。老回回攻破了东直门！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 19,
    "line_start": 9,
    "line_end": 9
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3925",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "永昌元年大顺王万万岁",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 19,
    "line_start": 9,
    "line_end": 9
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3926",
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "人心如此，闯王那得不成大事？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 19,
    "line_start": 9,
    "line_end": 9
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_3927",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "金蛇王，金蛇王，咱们破城啦！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 19,
    "line_start": 11,
    "line_end": 11
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_4291",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_sun_zhong_jun",
    "text": "贼婆娘，恶贱人",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 20,
    "line_start": 3,
    "line_end": 3
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_4292",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_sun_zhong_jun",
    "text": "咱们上去截住这小子，别让他跑了！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 20,
    "line_start": 3,
    "line_end": 3
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_4293",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "孙师姊不爱别人帮手，这小子她对付得了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 20,
    "line_start": 3,
    "line_end": 3
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_4294",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_sun_zhong_jun",
    "text": "你杀了我妻子和三个儿女，那也罢了，怎么连我七十多岁的老娘也都害了？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 20,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_4295",
    "speaker": "char_sun_zhong_jun",
    "speaker_name": "孙仲君",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你这种无耻狂徒，家里人再多些，也一起杀了！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 20,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_4296",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "孙师姑怎么不用剑？这单钩使来挺不顺手。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 20,
    "line_start": 7,
    "line_end": 7
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_4297",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_sun_zhong_jun",
    "text": "孙师姊，接剑！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 20,
    "line_start": 7,
    "line_end": 7
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_4298",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "孙师妹另练兵刃，她不用剑！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 20,
    "line_start": 7,
    "line_end": 7
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_4299",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_sun_zhong_jun",
    "text": "饶了他吧，好让师祖夸奖你。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 20,
    "line_start": 9,
    "line_end": 9
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_4300",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": "char_sun_zhong_jun",
    "text": "贼婆娘，臭贱人",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 20,
    "line_start": 11,
    "line_end": 11
  }
]